554
00:41:47,200 --> 00:41:50,080
Not only this, but you insulted me

555
00:41:50,160 --> 00:41:51,480
by snatching my wife!

556
00:41:59,200 --> 00:42:01,560
I'm scared. I'm not involved in this.

557
00:42:01,640 --> 00:42:05,120
My son only opened a factory.

558
00:42:05,200 --> 00:42:06,640
What did they do about it?

559
00:42:06,720 --> 00:42:08,360
Instead of saving my face

560
00:42:08,440 --> 00:42:10,880
and telling me about it,

561
00:42:10,960 --> 00:42:13,920
they got my son arrested.

562
00:42:14,000 --> 00:42:15,680
They are the ones

563
00:42:15,760 --> 00:42:17,520
who ruined my life.

564
00:42:19,280 --> 00:42:20,880
I don't know about this.

565
00:42:20,960 --> 00:42:24,320
I'm scared now. Please spare me.
I'm begging you.

566
00:42:24,400 --> 00:42:25,840
Where are you?

567
00:42:25,920 --> 00:42:27,240
Come out here now!

568
00:42:35,280 --> 00:42:36,600
That's Saruj's car.

569
00:42:46,040 --> 00:42:46,920
Saruj.

570
00:42:47,480 --> 00:42:48,360
Petch.

571
00:42:50,840 --> 00:42:51,720
Nava.

572
00:42:52,680 --> 00:42:55,760
He's inside your house in a rage.
He's shooting things.

573
00:42:55,840 --> 00:42:58,000
What did you say? Nava?

574
00:42:58,080 --> 00:42:59,440
Yes.

575
00:42:59,520 --> 00:43:01,160
-I'll take care of him.
-You can't.

576
00:43:01,240 --> 00:43:03,360
He's mad right now.
If he sees you two together,

577
00:43:03,440 --> 00:43:04,480
he'll shoot you.

578
00:43:06,360 --> 00:43:07,640
You have to get away.

579
00:43:15,160 --> 00:43:17,160
Tell everyone that a criminal broke in.

580
00:43:17,240 --> 00:43:18,960
Tell them not to come outside.

581
00:43:19,040 --> 00:43:20,600
-Okay.
-Go now.

582
00:43:20,680 --> 00:43:22,280
I've told Mr. Petch's family, Mr. Chat's,

583
00:43:22,360 --> 00:43:23,840
Mr. Jak's, Mr. Phu's.

584
00:43:23,920 --> 00:43:26,320
Who have I not told?

585
00:43:26,400 --> 00:43:27,400
It's…

586
00:43:28,440 --> 00:43:30,000
Madam Orn.

587
00:43:30,080 --> 00:43:32,320
What's all the noise, Jon?

588
00:43:32,400 --> 00:43:34,920
Jon, what's the noise?

589
00:43:35,440 --> 00:43:36,440
Madam Orn.

590
00:43:36,920 --> 00:43:38,240
You never come here.

591
00:43:38,320 --> 00:43:39,960
Why did you come here today?

592
00:43:41,160 --> 00:43:42,320
Madam Orn.

593
00:43:42,400 --> 00:43:44,200
It has been a while.

594
00:43:44,680 --> 00:43:46,080
Are you still alive?

595
00:43:46,840 --> 00:43:49,040
Mr. Chamnan,

596
00:43:49,680 --> 00:43:51,240
when did you get here?

597
00:43:51,320 --> 00:43:52,480
Who's Chamnan?

598
00:43:54,480 --> 00:43:55,760
Who are you here to see then?

599
00:43:55,840 --> 00:43:57,440
This is Chat's house.

600
00:43:57,520 --> 00:43:58,760
Are you here to see him?

601
00:43:58,840 --> 00:43:59,760
Who's Chat?

602
00:43:59,840 --> 00:44:01,160
I came here for Saruj.

603
00:44:01,240 --> 00:44:02,320
I'm here to get him.

604
00:44:06,040 --> 00:44:08,120
You're loved by everyone here.

605
00:44:08,200 --> 00:44:09,880
If I take you down,

606
00:44:09,960 --> 00:44:12,440
then that means I take all of you down.

607
00:44:12,520 --> 00:44:13,800
Am I right?

608
00:44:13,880 --> 00:44:14,760
That's not true.

609
00:44:14,840 --> 00:44:15,960
Mr. Nava.

610
00:44:16,040 --> 00:44:17,880
Please have mercy on her. I'm begging you.

611
00:44:25,800 --> 00:44:27,760
What's this black thing?

612
00:44:27,840 --> 00:44:29,960
Isn't this a gun?

613
00:44:30,040 --> 00:44:32,360
-Oh dear, you're an adult.
-Hey.

614
00:44:32,440 --> 00:44:35,040
Why are you still playing
with this kind of thing?

615
00:44:37,800 --> 00:44:38,920
Let me try it.

616
00:44:44,080 --> 00:44:45,880
My gosh.

617
00:44:46,440 --> 00:44:49,000
This is real.

618
00:44:49,080 --> 00:44:51,160
It's not a toy.

619
00:44:51,240 --> 00:44:52,440
That's right.

620
00:44:52,520 --> 00:44:53,920
You old hag! I'll…

621
00:44:57,200 --> 00:44:59,080
-I haven't hit you yet!
-Ma'am.

622
00:45:00,880 --> 00:45:02,280
Mr. Nava.

623
00:45:02,360 --> 00:45:04,160
Mr. Saruj really isn't here.

624
00:45:04,240 --> 00:45:05,720
Please let us go.

625
00:45:05,800 --> 00:45:06,840
No!

626
00:45:06,920 --> 00:45:10,080
I'm not leaving until I have Muslin.

627
00:45:15,240 --> 00:45:17,280
What's with the people in this palace?

628
00:45:17,360 --> 00:45:20,400
I'm speaking this loudly,
but not a single one has appeared!

629
00:45:22,160 --> 00:45:23,320
I'm here.

630
00:46:22,320 --> 00:46:23,320
Ma'am.

631
00:46:23,400 --> 00:46:24,640
Ma'am.

632
00:46:24,720 --> 00:46:26,320
Madam Orn.

633
00:46:26,400 --> 00:46:28,000
-Ma'am.
-Great-Grandma.

634
00:46:28,080 --> 00:46:29,760
Great-Grandma.

635
00:46:29,840 --> 00:46:31,240
He didn't hit her, did he?

636
00:46:31,320 --> 00:46:33,520
No, she probably just fainted.

637
00:46:34,440 --> 00:46:36,320
Great-Grandma.

638
00:46:36,880 --> 00:46:38,680
Are you hurt, Jon?

639
00:46:38,760 --> 00:46:39,920
No.

640
00:46:40,000 --> 00:46:41,600
Fortunately, Mr. Saruj isn't here.

641
00:46:41,680 --> 00:46:43,680
If he were,
he'd definitely have been shot.

642
00:46:43,760 --> 00:46:46,840
Saruj has taken Muslin to the airport.
He knows about this already.

643
00:46:46,920 --> 00:46:47,840
I see.

644
00:46:48,400 --> 00:46:50,360
Great-Grandma, get up slowly.

645
00:46:52,040 --> 00:46:53,280
Phu, Jon.

646
00:46:53,760 --> 00:46:55,040
What happened to Great-Grandma?

647
00:46:55,120 --> 00:46:56,120
She probably fainted.

648
00:47:02,880 --> 00:47:05,080
Where is Nava? Where did he go?

649
00:47:08,640 --> 00:47:10,440
He was lying right there.

650
00:47:11,080 --> 00:47:12,080
Where did he go?

651
00:47:12,160 --> 00:47:14,440
He's going to the airport to find Saruj.

652
00:47:26,520 --> 00:47:27,560
I got it.

653
00:47:27,640 --> 00:47:29,480
This is your ticket.

654
00:47:35,720 --> 00:47:37,920
How will you stay here if I leave?

655
00:47:38,000 --> 00:47:40,000
Nava is also after you.

656
00:47:40,480 --> 00:47:42,000
I'm going with you.

657
00:47:43,360 --> 00:47:44,520
This is my ticket.

658
00:47:50,400 --> 00:47:51,320
Really?

659
00:47:51,400 --> 00:47:53,360
Are you really coming with me?

660
00:47:53,920 --> 00:47:54,760
Yes.

661
00:48:02,800 --> 00:48:04,160
I know how you are.

662
00:48:04,960 --> 00:48:07,600
You won't be able to stay alone
at a time like this.

663
00:48:09,560 --> 00:48:11,160
I'm so happy.

664
00:48:11,920 --> 00:48:15,480
I'd go mad
if I had to go and stay by myself.

665
00:48:16,160 --> 00:48:17,680
The parliament will be dissolved soon.

666
00:48:17,760 --> 00:48:19,960
Mr. Danai won't be a minister anymore.

667
00:48:20,040 --> 00:48:22,360
I called him and requested to take leave.

668
00:48:22,920 --> 00:48:24,440
He remembers you.

669
00:48:33,040 --> 00:48:34,800
I only have you.

670
00:48:35,760 --> 00:48:37,880
You have always been by my side.

671
00:48:41,720 --> 00:48:43,040
You're crying again.

672
00:48:45,600 --> 00:48:46,920
Don't cry.

673
00:48:59,720 --> 00:49:01,000
If I have nothing left,

674
00:49:02,040 --> 00:49:03,840
then you'll have nothing left either.

675
00:49:08,440 --> 00:49:09,600
Muslin!

676
00:49:14,200 --> 00:49:15,440
Nava.

677
00:49:15,960 --> 00:49:18,360
Don't you dare think
of going anywhere together.

678
00:49:18,440 --> 00:49:19,760
If I have to die,

679
00:49:21,360 --> 00:49:22,480
then I'll take you with me.

680
00:49:26,440 --> 00:49:27,600
Saruj.

681
00:49:32,600 --> 00:49:33,440
Let go!

682
00:49:33,960 --> 00:49:35,560
In my capacity as a police officer,

683
00:49:35,640 --> 00:49:38,960
I'm arresting you for possession
of a firearm in a public place,

684
00:49:39,040 --> 00:49:42,000
for trespassing on Jutathep Palace,
and for attempted murder.

685
00:49:42,080 --> 00:49:44,480
These are serious charges.
You won't get away this time.

686
00:49:44,960 --> 00:49:46,840
Let go of me!

687
00:49:46,920 --> 00:49:48,480
We didn't do anything.

688
00:49:48,560 --> 00:49:50,000
You brought this on yourself.

689
00:49:53,240 --> 00:49:54,840
Have a safe trip, Saruj.

690
00:49:54,920 --> 00:49:56,920
Think of this as a vacation.

691
00:49:58,120 --> 00:49:59,360
Don't worry, Mus.

692
00:49:59,440 --> 00:50:01,240
After we've dealt with Nava,

693
00:50:01,320 --> 00:50:02,480
you'll get to come home.

694
00:50:02,560 --> 00:50:03,440
Thank you.

695
00:50:03,520 --> 00:50:04,960
Jutatheps always help each other.

696
00:50:05,040 --> 00:50:06,400
Give us time to take care of this,

697
00:50:06,480 --> 00:50:08,680
so you can come back
and lead your normal lives.

698
00:50:10,360 --> 00:50:11,960
I'm going to kill you all!

699
00:50:12,480 --> 00:50:13,520
Come with us.

700
00:50:13,600 --> 00:50:15,200
Let go! Why are you arresting me?

701
00:50:15,280 --> 00:50:17,480
Let go of me!

702
00:50:17,560 --> 00:50:18,840
I said let go!

703
00:50:19,320 --> 00:50:20,400
Let go!

704
00:50:22,960 --> 00:50:24,360
Thank you so much, guys.

705
00:50:25,960 --> 00:50:27,120
You should go.

706
00:50:39,800 --> 00:50:41,320
Good luck, Saruj.

707
00:50:49,800 --> 00:50:51,240
Ma'am.

708
00:50:54,560 --> 00:50:56,160
Ma'am.

709
00:50:56,240 --> 00:50:57,440
-Hey.
-Oh dear.

710
00:50:57,520 --> 00:50:59,280
Ma'am.

711
00:51:00,720 --> 00:51:01,960
Madam Orn.

712
00:51:03,800 --> 00:51:04,840
Madam Orn.

713
00:51:05,960 --> 00:51:07,360
How are you?

714
00:51:07,440 --> 00:51:08,400
Madam Orn.

715
00:51:10,040 --> 00:51:11,040
A gun.

716
00:51:11,120 --> 00:51:12,480
I shot a gun.

717
00:51:12,560 --> 00:51:15,040
Yes, but it's okay now.

718
00:51:15,120 --> 00:51:17,640
You're safe now. Mr. Nava has left.

719
00:51:18,520 --> 00:51:19,920
Not Nava.

720
00:51:20,000 --> 00:51:21,320
It was Chamnan.

721
00:51:21,400 --> 00:51:22,600
Which Chamnan?

722
00:51:24,520 --> 00:51:26,240
Yes, ma'am. It was Chamnan.

723
00:51:27,280 --> 00:51:28,320
Madam Orn.

724
00:51:28,800 --> 00:51:30,960
Are you hurt anywhere?

725
00:51:35,920 --> 00:51:36,840
No.

726
00:51:37,920 --> 00:51:38,960
So what happened?

727
00:51:39,760 --> 00:51:41,120
Why can't I remember?

728
00:51:41,200 --> 00:51:43,360
Well, back then,

729
00:51:43,440 --> 00:51:46,120
you were very calm,

730
00:51:46,200 --> 00:51:48,480
but you passed out
after you got surprised,

731
00:51:48,560 --> 00:51:50,560
and you landed on the floor smoothly,

732
00:51:50,640 --> 00:51:52,800
so you didn't get hit.

733
00:51:52,880 --> 00:51:55,000
Who was going to hit me? Chamnan?

734
00:51:55,560 --> 00:51:56,920
Nava.

735
00:51:57,000 --> 00:51:59,080
-Nava was also going to hit me?
-Yes, ma'am.

736
00:51:59,160 --> 00:52:01,040
Why is he so evil?

737
00:52:01,800 --> 00:52:04,120
I'll get my grandchildren
to deal with him.

738
00:52:04,200 --> 00:52:07,840
-Just you wait.
-Yes.

739
00:52:07,920 --> 00:52:09,120
Ms. Cheewan.

740
00:52:10,000 --> 00:52:11,960
Mr. Saruj has left.

741
00:52:12,040 --> 00:52:13,160
What?

742
00:52:13,240 --> 00:52:14,800
He's left?

743
00:52:15,680 --> 00:52:17,200
Where did he go?

744
00:52:21,160 --> 00:52:23,400
Saruj asked me to tell you

745
00:52:23,480 --> 00:52:26,680
that he is going to take care of Muslin,
so don't worry about him.

746
00:52:26,760 --> 00:52:29,200
What does he mean by taking care of her?

747
00:52:29,280 --> 00:52:30,920
Is that all he said?

748
00:52:32,760 --> 00:52:35,760
Didn't he leave me a letter or anything?

749
00:52:36,600 --> 00:52:39,200
He asked me to pack some stuff
and take it to the airport.

750
00:52:40,120 --> 00:52:42,360
He was flying to Europe with her.

751
00:52:42,440 --> 00:52:45,120
He's taken leave

752
00:52:45,200 --> 00:52:46,680
but didn't say for how long.

753
00:52:46,760 --> 00:52:48,280
He didn't say for how long?

754
00:52:50,360 --> 00:52:52,680
Saruj left his job?

755
00:52:52,760 --> 00:52:54,640
For Mrs. Mus?

756
00:52:56,280 --> 00:52:57,120
Yes.

757
00:52:57,600 --> 00:52:59,400
Everything was in a rush.

758
00:53:00,200 --> 00:53:03,680
Even though we caught Nava,

759
00:53:03,760 --> 00:53:07,160
the legal process will take a month,

760
00:53:07,800 --> 00:53:11,280
and Nava can live his life
like normal in the meantime.

761
00:53:11,800 --> 00:53:14,360
He might take revenge on them

762
00:53:14,440 --> 00:53:17,920
or might skip bail and go abroad.

763
00:53:20,440 --> 00:53:21,840
Is it that bad?

764
00:53:23,040 --> 00:53:25,440
Couldn't he even call me?

765
00:53:30,560 --> 00:53:32,320
Are you okay, Cheewan?

766
00:53:37,600 --> 00:53:39,640
I never told him.

767
00:53:40,200 --> 00:53:43,120
I've been meaning to tell him for days,

768
00:53:43,200 --> 00:53:45,320
but I never said it.

769
00:53:47,120 --> 00:53:48,320
Why?

770
00:53:48,840 --> 00:53:52,040
Why didn't I tell him?

771
00:53:52,120 --> 00:53:53,480
What do you want to say?

772
00:53:54,760 --> 00:53:57,240
What if he doesn't come back?

773
00:53:57,320 --> 00:53:59,520
What if he never comes back?

774
00:54:03,080 --> 00:54:05,360
If you're afraid I'll get back together
with her,

775
00:54:06,360 --> 00:54:08,000
then tell me you love me.

776
00:54:08,080 --> 00:54:09,400
That's got nothing to do with it.

777
00:54:09,480 --> 00:54:12,760
If you say you love me,

778
00:54:12,840 --> 00:54:16,280
I'll keep my heart

779
00:54:16,360 --> 00:54:18,360
for you only.

780
00:54:21,960 --> 00:54:23,120
How many times?

781
00:54:24,160 --> 00:54:26,360
How many times
have you done this, Cheewan?

782
00:54:26,440 --> 00:54:29,480
Why is it so difficult for you to say it?

783
00:54:30,200 --> 00:54:31,320
Why?

784
00:54:31,400 --> 00:54:34,640
Why didn't you just say it?

785
00:54:41,440 --> 00:54:42,480
It's okay.

786
00:54:51,400 --> 00:54:54,000
What if I don't get another chance?

787
00:54:56,600 --> 00:54:58,720
What if he doesn't come back?

788
00:54:59,400 --> 00:55:01,840
What if he never comes back?

789
00:55:04,440 --> 00:55:05,560
Why?

790
00:55:06,120 --> 00:55:08,520
-Why am I so stupid?
-Don't do this.

791
00:55:08,600 --> 00:55:10,880
-Gosh, Cheewan.
-Calm down.

792
00:55:49,960 --> 00:55:51,040
This apartment

793
00:55:51,120 --> 00:55:54,200
is usually used by the embassy.

794
00:55:54,760 --> 00:55:56,000
It's safe for us.

795
00:55:58,880 --> 00:56:00,200
Is it okay for you?

796
00:56:00,760 --> 00:56:01,880
Yes.

797
00:56:03,000 --> 00:56:05,120
I can stay anywhere if you're with me.

798
00:56:19,360 --> 00:56:22,840
You take the big room.
I'll take the small room upstairs.

799
00:56:25,440 --> 00:56:27,840
We were just in Thailand this morning.

800
00:56:27,920 --> 00:56:30,000
I don't know how we ended up here.

801
00:56:31,720 --> 00:56:35,520
Everything happened so fast.
I'm still in shock.

802
00:56:37,240 --> 00:56:38,920
I expected this would happen.

803
00:56:40,400 --> 00:56:42,320
We finally got in trouble.

804
00:56:45,040 --> 00:56:46,160
Get some rest.

805
00:56:48,080 --> 00:56:49,840
We'll go out
to get something to eat later.

806
00:57:10,520 --> 00:57:11,840
It's all done.

807
00:57:21,360 --> 00:57:22,760
I just got bailed out.

808
00:57:23,480 --> 00:57:25,960
Do you know what the first thing
I'm going to do is?

809
00:57:27,200 --> 00:57:28,640
Take a rest?

810
00:57:28,720 --> 00:57:30,200
Listen to a sermon?

811
00:57:31,000 --> 00:57:34,160
Follow Saruj and Muslin
to the other side of the world.

812
00:57:34,240 --> 00:57:36,120
I still have some connections.

813
00:57:36,200 --> 00:57:38,120
I'll eventually find them.

814
00:57:38,200 --> 00:57:41,360
They'll never get to live in peace.

815
00:57:59,440 --> 00:58:02,520
Is that why Saruj can't come back?

816
00:58:03,960 --> 00:58:05,960
But it has been three weeks now.

817
00:58:06,680 --> 00:58:09,560
You see, Mr. Danai, his boss,

818
00:58:09,640 --> 00:58:11,760
asked him
to take care of something abroad.

819
00:58:12,360 --> 00:58:14,920
Meanwhile, he's keeping
Saruj's address a secret.

820
00:58:15,000 --> 00:58:16,720
I don't think he'll contact us.

821
00:58:16,800 --> 00:58:18,560
He'll only contact Mr. Danai.

822
00:58:19,080 --> 00:58:22,920
Does this mean
none of you knows Saruj's address?

823
00:58:25,560 --> 00:58:26,680
Yes.

824
00:58:27,240 --> 00:58:29,320
What if Mr. Nava finds him?

825
00:58:29,400 --> 00:58:31,520
What if he gets sick or--

826
00:58:31,600 --> 00:58:33,440
Calm down, Cheewan.

827
00:58:33,520 --> 00:58:35,040
I think he'll come back soon.

828
00:58:39,160 --> 00:58:41,000
Nava was acquitted

829
00:58:41,480 --> 00:58:42,800
in the collapsed condo case.

830
00:58:43,920 --> 00:58:45,760
But he's facing
other much more serious charges.

831
00:58:49,960 --> 00:58:51,520
We'll do our best

832
00:58:51,600 --> 00:58:53,320
to bring Saruj back to Thailand.

833
00:59:13,960 --> 00:59:15,520
Are you going to work?

834
00:59:16,080 --> 00:59:17,200
Yes.

835
00:59:17,280 --> 00:59:19,560
Are you going to leave me here alone?

836
00:59:19,640 --> 00:59:21,080
There's a Thai temple near here.

837
00:59:21,160 --> 00:59:24,800
I'll take you there so you can make
some friends and have something to do.

838
00:59:24,880 --> 00:59:27,440
What if they recognize me?

839
00:59:27,520 --> 00:59:30,320
I don't want to listen to their gossip.

840
00:59:31,400 --> 00:59:34,160
I'd rather not. I don't want to go.

841
00:59:34,240 --> 00:59:38,120
I'll stay here and do some housework
and cook while I wait for you.

842
00:59:38,200 --> 00:59:39,480
Okay.

843
00:59:59,160 --> 01:00:00,560
I MISS YOU, SARUJ. CAN YOU REPLY?

844
01:00:10,920 --> 01:00:12,160
Answer me.

845
01:00:27,240 --> 01:00:28,160
Gosh.

846
01:00:28,760 --> 01:00:29,680
Gosh.

847
01:00:30,600 --> 01:00:33,280
Please slow down. I can't catch them all.

848
01:00:35,840 --> 01:00:39,440
Jon, catch them.
The bael fruits are getting bruised.

849
01:00:46,920 --> 01:00:48,200
Jon.

850
01:00:48,280 --> 01:00:50,520
I don't know
where she gets the energy from.

851
01:00:50,600 --> 01:00:52,000
She's so active.

852
01:00:52,080 --> 01:00:53,160
Cheewan.

853
01:00:54,040 --> 01:00:55,720
Why are you picking so much?

854
01:00:55,800 --> 01:00:58,360
Madam Orn gave me a recipe.
I want to try it out.

855
01:01:02,160 --> 01:01:03,160
What's wrong with her?

856
01:01:03,880 --> 01:01:05,160
She looks stressed.

857
01:01:05,240 --> 01:01:08,160
She has been like this
since Mr. Saruj left a month ago.

858
01:01:16,840 --> 01:01:18,160
-Jon.
-Yes?

859
01:01:18,240 --> 01:01:20,160
Don't mention his name again. Got it?

860
01:01:21,240 --> 01:01:22,560
I don't want to hear his name.

861
01:01:23,600 --> 01:01:25,440
He's so selfish.

862
01:01:25,520 --> 01:01:27,240
He hasn't sent me a single letter.

863
01:01:27,320 --> 01:01:29,760
Is he not going to contact us at all?

864
01:01:31,520 --> 01:01:33,440
There are people after him.

865
01:01:33,520 --> 01:01:34,880
He isn't there for a holiday.

866
01:01:34,960 --> 01:01:36,920
It's difficult for him to do anything.

867
01:01:37,480 --> 01:01:39,480
You men are all the same.

868
01:01:39,560 --> 01:01:40,880
You all take his side.

869
01:01:40,960 --> 01:01:42,760
He won't come back

870
01:01:42,840 --> 01:01:45,000
because he's obsessed with that woman.

871
01:01:45,080 --> 01:01:46,760
He said there was nothing between them,

872
01:01:46,840 --> 01:01:48,960
but they ran away together.

873
01:01:49,040 --> 01:01:51,600
It's not like that. He loves you a lot.

874
01:01:51,680 --> 01:01:53,160
He'll come back soon.

875
01:01:54,040 --> 01:01:56,680
He'll forget about his home

876
01:01:56,760 --> 01:01:57,800
and everyone here

877
01:01:57,880 --> 01:01:59,360
and won't come back again.

878
01:02:11,320 --> 01:02:12,360
Cheewan.

879
01:02:20,920 --> 01:02:22,000
Here,

880
01:02:22,080 --> 01:02:23,440
your reward.

881
01:02:26,600 --> 01:02:30,440
Muslin always seems to irritate you.

882
01:02:31,040 --> 01:02:32,480
It must be because…

883
01:02:38,320 --> 01:02:40,360
JEALOUS

884
01:02:40,440 --> 01:02:43,640
Hey! I said I'm not jealous.

885
01:02:43,720 --> 01:02:45,160
I'm not. Take it back.

886
01:02:55,640 --> 01:02:56,760
Everything…

887
01:02:58,040 --> 01:02:59,640
seems to remind me of him.

888
01:03:00,440 --> 01:03:02,680
When you love someone a lot,

889
01:03:02,760 --> 01:03:04,080
you don't use this.

890
01:03:06,120 --> 01:03:07,360
But…

891
01:03:10,320 --> 01:03:11,800
When you love someone a lot…

892
01:03:13,200 --> 01:03:14,680
but they don't return your feelings…

893
01:03:15,240 --> 01:03:16,920
your heart gets shaken.

894
01:03:17,400 --> 01:03:18,240
You feel anxious…

895
01:03:19,400 --> 01:03:21,040
and restless.

896
01:03:36,560 --> 01:03:38,440
It hurts right here.

897
01:03:39,640 --> 01:03:41,640
The more I think of him,

898
01:03:42,360 --> 01:03:44,240
the more it hurts.

899
01:03:45,400 --> 01:03:48,120
When I think
that he's in love with someone else…

900
01:03:50,640 --> 01:03:52,440
it hurts even more.

901
01:03:54,320 --> 01:03:56,240
I can't stand being alone

902
01:03:57,240 --> 01:03:59,640
without him by my side.

903
01:04:00,320 --> 01:04:03,120
That's why you've been trying
to keep yourself occupied,

904
01:04:03,880 --> 01:04:05,680
so it won't hurt so much, right?

905
01:04:08,720 --> 01:04:10,480
When you love someone a lot

906
01:04:11,160 --> 01:04:13,160
but they're not by your side,

907
01:04:13,240 --> 01:04:15,080
your heart just feels empty.

908
01:04:15,600 --> 01:04:17,760
When you love someone a lot,

909
01:04:17,840 --> 01:04:19,760
but they don't return your feelings…

910
01:04:21,280 --> 01:04:22,560
in here feels empty.

911
01:04:24,160 --> 01:04:26,280
You feel like giving up on life.

912
01:04:27,320 --> 01:04:28,600
I used to think…

913
01:04:30,080 --> 01:04:32,120
that being single

914
01:04:33,280 --> 01:04:35,200
or traveling the world

915
01:04:36,320 --> 01:04:38,760
were my biggest dreams.

916
01:04:40,360 --> 01:04:41,840
But then he came into my life.

917
01:04:43,280 --> 01:04:46,840
I can't live by myself anymore.

918
01:04:47,480 --> 01:04:49,920
Why is it like this, Cheewa?

919
01:04:53,280 --> 01:04:54,280
Why?

920
01:04:56,720 --> 01:04:58,240
Why, Cheewa?

921
01:05:27,560 --> 01:05:29,640
Excuse me. I have a question.

922
01:05:29,720 --> 01:05:33,680
If I want to send a postcard to a member
of staff who is posted overseas,

923
01:05:33,760 --> 01:05:35,520
where should I send it?

924
01:05:35,600 --> 01:05:39,680
You can send it to the Thai embassy.
Which country is it? I'll get the address.

925
01:05:41,400 --> 01:05:43,080
I'm sending one to every country.

926
01:05:43,160 --> 01:05:45,280
Every country?

927
01:05:45,920 --> 01:05:47,000
Okay.

928
01:05:47,080 --> 01:05:48,440
-Sure.
-Please help me.

929
01:06:19,120 --> 01:06:21,000
You must listen to your heart from now on.

930
01:06:21,080 --> 01:06:22,440
If you can't escape it,

931
01:06:23,040 --> 01:06:24,600
and you can't stop loving them,

932
01:06:24,680 --> 01:06:26,080
then just give in to it.

933
01:06:27,560 --> 01:06:29,360
I gave in a long time ago.

934
01:06:30,840 --> 01:06:32,720
I have no other choice…

935
01:06:34,160 --> 01:06:35,320
but to fight.

936
01:06:38,280 --> 01:06:39,280
Fight.

937
01:07:07,960 --> 01:07:09,680
-Hello.
-Hello.

938
01:07:09,760 --> 01:07:11,960
-Please give these documents to Mr. Saruj.
-Okay.

939
01:07:12,040 --> 01:07:14,680
There are some letters
and a postcard as well.

940
01:07:14,760 --> 01:07:15,880
Thank you.

941
01:07:37,960 --> 01:07:39,640
I love you, Saruj.

942
01:07:39,720 --> 01:07:41,440
Please come back to Thailand.

943
01:07:58,840 --> 01:08:01,240
Mus, did someone from the embassy drop by?

944
01:08:01,720 --> 01:08:02,680
Yes.

945
01:08:30,319 --> 01:08:31,920
She brought you some documents.

946
01:08:33,080 --> 01:08:34,000
Thank you.

947
01:08:45,439 --> 01:08:46,720
Thank you.

948
01:09:06,760 --> 01:09:07,960
Cheewa!

949
01:09:08,520 --> 01:09:09,479
Cheewa!

950
01:09:11,040 --> 01:09:12,920
What is it, Cheewan?

951
01:09:13,800 --> 01:09:16,000
I got this address from a member of staff.

952
01:09:16,080 --> 01:09:19,120
She said Saruj would be here
for a meeting and for work.

953
01:09:20,439 --> 01:09:23,640
Gosh. Date, time, and meeting venue?

954
01:09:23,720 --> 01:09:24,720
Did you get it all?

955
01:09:24,800 --> 01:09:25,840
Yes.

956
01:09:37,240 --> 01:09:38,720
I want to go there.

957
01:09:58,840 --> 01:10:01,400
You don't want me to aim high

958
01:10:01,960 --> 01:10:03,680
because you're afraid I might get hurt.

959
01:10:03,760 --> 01:10:05,520
If I have a chance to find love,

960
01:10:05,600 --> 01:10:07,160
but it means I might get hurt…

961
01:10:08,640 --> 01:10:10,640
I still think it'll be worth it.

962
01:10:11,840 --> 01:10:14,160
If I don't fight for my love

963
01:10:14,720 --> 01:10:16,280
or get to confess my love,

964
01:10:16,840 --> 01:10:19,120
all I'll feel is pain.

965
01:10:19,200 --> 01:10:21,800
This is the last day.
You should go and enjoy yourselves.

966
01:10:24,480 --> 01:10:26,560
Someone is waiting for you at the museum.

967
01:10:26,640 --> 01:10:29,080
She said she's your sister from Thailand.

968
01:10:29,160 --> 01:10:31,840
Saruj has always shown me

969
01:10:32,400 --> 01:10:34,040
that he loves me.

970
01:10:35,240 --> 01:10:36,600
But I

971
01:10:36,680 --> 01:10:40,040
have never told him I love him.

972
01:11:05,840 --> 01:11:10,840
Subtitle translation by: Tanida Itthiwat

